{"tid":1584380,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[分析] 點解合法遊行要封鐵?","createTime":"2019-09-21T05:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T06:04:40.000Z","uid":112814,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"56bd284951b2292245e05eeac0d144794aa7c3d9","tid":1584380,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:43:22.000Z","msg":"因為合法遊行係有糾察數人頭 政府依3個月出盡奶力都阻唔到人上街 turning point係818黑警行錯步柒棋就係批准集會 然後170萬人終極和平集會贏盡輿論 打腫左政府同黑警塊面<br />\n<br />\n所以政府同黑警係極不爽 然後接落黎依個月基本上一係就反對遊行 一係就封鐵封路 除左阻撚住我哋之外<br />\n最大目的就係形造少人遊行既假象<br />\n然後再用輿論洗版吹風話示威退潮   其實就係想做假數俾國際同其他人睇 話我哋輸緊 <br />\n亦都係想動搖我地軍心<br />\n可惜就連915都成幾廿萬人出黎 又打爆銅記 9 8美領又幾廿萬人<br />\n證明我哋已經有起碼30萬人基本盤<br />\n係唔會屈服"},{"pid":"9f6aafd492802243e1a024464a1c6c1bc87303d2","tid":1584380,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:44:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"af62045c03351b3686fda8cab420f436d7a74f35","tid":1584380,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"係港島搞佢唔敢封鐵"},{"pid":"7ecda7302cbb3d2dd334b3eca91a9977b0a1988f","tid":1584380,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"睇下佢封唔封九龍塘"},{"pid":"8a2fef7604187c7d477910e8beade7e90deea9c2","tid":1584380,"uid":136992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DVaCivo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDVaCivo.jpg&h=ff195ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sm8PT3N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSm8PT3N.png&h=cb597f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/